{"tid":1845374,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"盛康區 選舉呈請進度【第2彈】","createTime":"2020-01-27T06:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T06:34:11.000Z","uid":268430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0a984aa030860d9213c12a2b286ad37772e442d8","tid":1845374,"uid":268430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:27:25.000Z","msg":"funding link<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/appeal-%e9%81%b8%e8%88%89%e5%91%88%e8%ab%8b/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fappeal-%25e9%2581%25b8%25e8%2588%2589%25e5%2591%2588%25e8%25ab%258b%2F&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RhR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=8301747e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/appeal-%e9%81%b8%e8%88%89%e5%91%88%e8%ab%8b/</a><br />\n<br />\n各位新年進步 <br />\n<br />\n同大家交代 1月29日（星期三）係最後一日可以遞交選舉呈請.   <br />\n<br />\n過去兩個月盛康區的趙姑娘一直聯絡居民搵資料 和收取律師法律意見。 1月14號律師再次提出可以作第一步呈請 - 檢票問題。<br />\n<br />\n過去個多星期聯絡過守護公義基金 關於衆籌， 因為時間太緊迫 ，今天傍晚建議開立一個衆籌戶口 ，靠各位居民 區議員幫忙  連登 推出去衆籌.   <br />\n<br />\n1/  首要衆籌$300,000 - 律師去信選舉呈請檢查有問題544票。 <br />\n2/  律師再根據檢票結果, 再續出第二部呈請,所以衆籌目標超過$1,000,000. <br />\n3/  律師決定無法再繼續第二段呈請， 扣除呈請開支，衆籌餘額會捐去： 612，守護公義基金及 星火（新捐款戶口/方法）"},{"pid":"609d9c9f4cd7913055673476cf7f30befd4f3a3c","tid":1845374,"uid":5777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:31:30.000Z","msg":"要咁多錢架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488b345c4e895a1cf748d285ab1214fa2614f050","tid":1845374,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T06:34:11.000Z","msg":"大數據專家李鴻彥：怒轟無能港共害死醫護 主流民意撐罷工聲響徹 武漢肺炎變政治災難<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eOcdQS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eOcdQS</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/84161729_2668909726538622_4384369973728903168_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_ohc=w1VKkGYytr0AX8CrirR&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=766eacade1e006a4044a55627b19160d&amp;oe=5EC6A255\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/83774346_2821123161273391_7906363059050905600_n.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;_nc_ohc=jUHmF-Eykq4AX8J-5xQ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=8f602cc6767e5bb308ecb84e436d47ad&amp;oe=5EC89D28\" />"}]}